# ============================================================
# DO NOT IGNORE - THESE ARE NEEDED IN REPO
# ============================================================
# ✅ KEEP: Model files (required for gesture recognition)
# ✅ KEEP: requirements.txt (Python dependencies)
# ✅ KEEP: pubspec.yaml & pubspec.lock (Flutter dependencies)
# ✅ KEEP: All documentation (README, SETUP, etc.)
# ✅ KEEP: All source code (lib/, ml_training/*)
# ✅ KEEP: Configuration files (analysis_options.yaml, etc.)

# These should NEVER be in gitignore:
!.gitkeep
!ml_training/models/gesture_model.pkl
!ml_training/models/sign_mapping.json
!ml_training/requirements.txt
!pubspec.yaml
!pubspec.lock
!README.md
!SETUP_FOR_GROUPMATES.md
!TROUBLESHOOTING.md
!QUICK_REFERENCE.md
!FILE_STRUCTURE.md
!NETWORK_CONFIGURATION_GUIDE.md
